                            <h6>Formatting Services</h6>
                            <h1>No-Stress Formatting<br/> and File Prep</h1>
                            <p>Kirkus' formatting services deliver polished, professional, and technically prepared files for both print and e-book publication through any platform, from Amazon’s Kindle Direct Publishing to IngramSpark to B&N Press and beyond. We guarantee your files will meet your platform’s publishing specifications.</p>
                            <p>Forget about becoming a publishing expert or muddling through the frustration.<br/>
                            <strong>Trust Kirkus to format your files and get you on your way to publication.</strong></p>

